    "en": {
      "title": "Pohottu supporters are looking for those who pushed Beira",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An operation has been started by the police to find the group that pushed a group of MPs including Pohottuwe into the Beira lake.",
        "After a group attacked the Colombo Galle Mudoora activists, a violent group dragged more than 20 people into the Beira lake and subjected them to various harassment on the 9th of May last.",
        "A person who allegedly robbed a local council member of money and pushed him into the Beira lake was recently arrested in the Wakanda area of \u200b\u200bColombo.",
        "This person, who has been arrested by the Colombo Crime Division, is a 34-year-old resident of Dematagoda area.",
        "The police said that while the MP was traveling in a bus, a group of people including the suspect dropped him and robbed him of his wallet and then pushed him into the Beira lake.",
        "The police are continuing investigations to find the other people who pushed the people into the Beira lake",
        "According to police sources, the person who was arrested will be questioned further in this regard."
      ],
